my-trading
==========

This repository contains only my own code (trading strategies, configs, and a small
dashboard overlay). It orchestrates several third-party projects that I do NOT
maintain or redistribute as source — they are pulled at runtime as Docker images,
referenced by pinned digest in docker-compose.yml.

Upstream projects referenced
----------------------------
- hummingbot-api — https://github.com/hummingbot/hummingbot-api
    Image: hummingbot/hummingbot-api  (Apache License 2.0)
- dashboard     — https://github.com/hummingbot/dashboard
    Image: hummingbot/dashboard       (Apache License 2.0)
- hummingbot-mcp (optional) — https://github.com/hummingbot/hummingbot-mcp
    Image: hummingbot/mcp             (Apache License 2.0)
- EMQX          — https://github.com/emqx/emqx        Image: emqx:5   (Apache License 2.0)
- PostgreSQL    — https://github.com/postgres/postgres Image: postgres:16 (PostgreSQL License)

